  <div style=3D"display: none; max-height: 0px; overflow: hidden;">Welcome =
to your latest installment of Wall Power, my twice-weekly dispatch from the=
 salerooms of the world=E2=80=99s leading auction houses. All weekend=E2=80=
=94at Phillips and Bonhams, Sotheby=E2=80=99s and Christie=E2=80=99s=E2=80=
=94the previews were packed. Last night, the presale crowds at Sotheby=E2=
=80=99s were larger and livelier than in recent memory. Many dealers and ar=
t advisors who don=E2=80=99t even buy modern and contemporary art were on h=
and to gauge the mood. And if the bidding in the room was any indication, t=
hey=E2=80=99re eager to wade back into the market=E2=80=94if only they can =
find the right material to bid on.
  =20
